{"tid":1545092,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"譚香文既「反自動當選運動」，９個有５個都同泛民／地區組織撞區，想點？","createTime":"2019-09-05T19:38:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-06T11:21:40.000Z","uid":63053,"like":34,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"43d1e9ad9a39d8bf573b06f727b875fcfb4d76d6","tid":1545092,"uid":63053,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T19:38:32.000Z","msg":"岩岩睇到另一個post講泛民支持既任嘉兒俾佢地撞走左，<br />\n明明早過佢地宣傳，又係當區居民<br />\n點解會俾個住西貢既迫走左？<br />\n再睇下個「反自動當選運動」係咩料<br />\n屌你<br />\n原來９個入面撞左５個<br />\n你係反自動當選運動　定係　鎅票運動？<br />\n明明白區仲有１５個，點解唔走去選？<br />\n<br />\n仲有，佢地立場都好可疑<br />\n撞走人果個歐頌賢<br />\n睇佢ＦＢ有人問佢對五大訴求睇法<br />\n佢兜圈死都唔答<br />\n有咩可能連咁基本既野都唔講支持？<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/V71fvxZ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FV71fvxZ.png&h=017ed1c6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"cc23c53f248a5b8559ddc5c1042b3748c4156272","tid":1545092,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T19:38:47.000Z","msg":"[行動post] 肯入黎睇9.7點樣揸機場輸精管未 | LIHKG <br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1</a> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/reLz9Yb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FreLz9Yb.jpg&h=bc5ea362&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VeJJ3id.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVeJJ3id.jpg&h=50bde3c1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"91a5f5ea9b21ff466e6735471f2b159d09fe74da","tid":1545092,"uid":63053,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T19:41:07.000Z","msg":"「反自動當選運動」發起人，除左譚香文，仲有另一個人<br />\n但係佢接受訪問竟然唔敢講全名，咩玩法？<br />\n<br />\n＂運動另一名發起人、不欲提供全名的蔡先生稱，正約見「撞區」一方見面，若「傾唔掂」建議搞初選。＂<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/article/20190810/s00001/1565441784917/%E3%80%90%E5%8D%80%E8%AD%B0%E6%9C%83%E9%81%B8%E8%88%89%E3%80%91%E3%80%8C%E5%8F%8D%E8%87%AA%E5%8B%95%E7